a.n: One Day With - Victoria, Saint Petersbourg

p.k: This new episode of One day with presents the private life of one of the new Playboy TV Europe models: the Russian Victoria Lesovaya! From the morning, spending some time in bed before getting up, until the evening, posing for a professional photo session. In order to keep feet, Victoria also practices some exercises in the park. Today we also accompany her on her first lesson of pottery, where she can make her own plate with the help of a special friend. She still has time to walk around Saint Petersburg in a beautiful sunny day and even admire the city from above, direct from a rooftop. In the end, as a bonus, a very sensual – and wet – performance! Come with her and don’t miss anything from her everyday life!
